WEBVTT

00:00:07.141 --> 00:00:08.905
Eh, romantik muhabbat,

00:00:08.905 --> 00:00:10.839
ba'zan maftunkor va sarmast qiluvchi,

00:00:10.839 --> 00:00:13.259
ba'zan yurakni parchalovchi va jafokash,

00:00:13.259 --> 00:00:15.357
ko'pincha esa hammasi birda.
Nima uchun

00:00:15.357 --> 00:00:18.919
biz hissiyotlarimizni siqib, suvidan 
sharbat qilishlariga qo'yib beramiz?

00:00:18.919 --> 00:00:21.201
Sevgi hayotimizga mazmun kiritadimi

00:00:21.201 --> 00:00:24.444
yoki yolg'izlik va azob-uqubatlardan 
qochmoqchi bo'lamizmi?

00:00:24.444 --> 00:00:26.705
Sevgi ortida jinsiy xohish-istagimiz

00:00:26.705 --> 00:00:30.409
yashiringanmi yoki bu nasl qoldirishimiz
uchun tabiat o'ylab topgan nayrangmi?